title: She named Cheryl Mills Benghazi dead "Stupid soldiers" in the leaked e-mail.
subtitle: There's no leaked e-mail in which Clinton long ago called Cheryl Mills dead Benghazi "stupid soldiers" and expressed her pleasure in torturing them.
author: Kim LaCapria
vclaim: The leaked e-mail revealed that Cheryl Mills' assistant Clinton called the men who died in Benghazi "stupid soldiers" and said she was happy to torture them.
